data.description: Amazing 3 years new home in gated community, within walking distance to Westgate Entertainment District. Split, spacious open floorplan. 3 bedrooms plus den, 10' ceilings throughout (including garage) with 8' interior doors. Modern kitchen with white 42'' cabinets, pots/pans drawers, gas range, custom Herringbone style tile backsplash, and large island with beautiful granite countertops. This gorgeous home boasts upgraded plush carpets in all 3 bedrooms. You will fall in love with beautiful curb appeal, Spanish style architecture, and paved driveway . Property backs to community walking path with partial fencing view.
